                                 {AA, BB, Q, Z, VEC} = qz(A,B):
                                 Q# * A * Z = AA:
                                 Q# * B * Z = BB:
                                 val = diag2vec(AA) ./ diag2vec(BB):
                                 A * VEC = B * VEC * vec2diag(val):
                                Matrix  AA: Upper triangular matrix
                                Matrix  BB: Upper triangular matrix
                                Matrix   Q: Orthogonal or unitary matrix
                                Matrix   Z: Orthogonal or unitary matrix
                                Matrix VEC: Generalized eigenvectors
                                Matrix val: Generalized eigenvalues
